                    </div>
                    <div class="mc-field-group">
                        <label for="mce-FNAME">First Name </label>
                        <input type="text" value="" name="FNAME" class="" id="mce-FNAME">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mc-field-group input-group">
                        <b>Please email me about: </b>
                        <ul><li><input type="checkbox" value="1" name="group[6335][1]" id="mce-group[6335]-6335-0"><label for="mce-group[6335]-6335-0">Weekly Comic Updates</label></li>
                            <li><input type="checkbox" value="2" name="group[6335][2]" id="mce-group[6335]-6335-1"><label for="mce-group[6335]-6335-1">New Merch &amp; Sales</label></li>
                            <li><input type="checkbox" value="4" name="group[6335][4]" id="mce-group[6335]-6335-2"><label for="mce-group[6335]-6335-2">News &amp; Kickstarters</label></li>
                        </ul>
                </div>
                <span>Unsure of what kind of content you'll receive? Not to worry! You can always <a href="https://us14.campaign-archive.com/home/?u=1019a29148e4e5193c1f0bbdd&id=6612f3a2e9" title="View previous campaigns">view our previous emails</a>.</span>
                    <div class="content__gdprLegal">
                        <p>We use Mailchimp as our marketing platform. By clicking below to subscribe, you acknowledge that your information will be transferred to Mailchimp for processing. <a href="https://mailchimp.com/legal/" target="_blank">Learn more about Mailchimp's privacy practices here.</a></p>
                    </div>
                <div id="mce-responses" class="clear">
                    <div class="response" id="mce-error-response" style="display:none"></div>
                    <div class="response" id="mce-success-response" style="display:none"></div>
                </div>    <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->
                <div style="position: absolute; left: -5000px;" aria-hidden="true"><input type="text" name="b_1019a29148e4e5193c1f0bbdd_6612f3a2e9" tabindex="-1" value=""></div>
                <div class="clear"><input type="submit" value="Subscribe" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="button"></div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <!--End mc_embed_signup-->
</div>
